One of the really fun parts of Roblox is getting to customize your character! Unfortunately, some of the customization is going to set you back quite a bit of Robux. That's the great part about promo codes, because they will give you some fun looking cosmetics for your avatar and they are completely free!

Newest Events & Free Items in Roblox
Here's where we keep track of all the new stuff that's going on in Roblox. If you can get something free and it has been added recently, it will most likely appear below!

Alo Sanctuary is a relaxing, yoga-focused experience that allows players to explore a tranquil map, participate in yoga classes using various collectable poses, and even earn a handful of exclusive free items. For a closer look at these items, and a rundown on how to unlock them, check out our guide below!

The second installment of the NFL x Roblox collaboration, NFL Tycoon allows players to build their own stadium, manage their dream team, and grow their franchise dynasty. To many player's delight, this experience also offers a handful of NFL-themed avatar items that can be claimed for free by completing a few short quests. For a closer look at these items, and a rundown on how to unlock them, check out our guide below!
